title: Nick Overhead
text:
Nicholas John Overhead (born 1942), is a male former athlete who competed for England.
Athletics career.
He represented <a href="England%20at%20the%201962%20British%20Empire%20and%20Commonwealth%20Games">England</a> in the 440 yards at the <a href="1962%20British%20Empire%20and%20Commonwealth%20Games">1962 British Empire and Commonwealth Games</a> in <a href="Perth">Perth</a>, Western Australia.
He was a member of the Watford Harriers Club.
